                    "description": "Highly reactive trace species: k_OH = 1.0e-16 m^3/s, the upper end of the upstream docstring's stated k_OH range (1e-10 cm^3/molec/s). OH_conc at the default. k_eff = 9.999999999999999e-05 s^-1, tau_OH = 10000.0 s (2.78 hours) \u2014 the short-lived end of the docstring's 'seconds to years' span. Representative of fast-oxidising species (many alkenes, terpenes) that are destroyed within hours of emission.",
