                    "description": "Clean remote atmosphere: OH_conc lowered to 1.0e11 m^-3 (~1e5 molec/cm^3, an order of magnitude below the global mean), k_OH at the CH4 default. k_eff = 6.3e-10 s^-1, tau_OH = 1587301587.3015873 s (50.30 yr). With little OH available the methane lifetime stretches tenfold \u2014 illustrating that the OH-reaction lifetime is set jointly by species reactivity and the ambient oxidant burden.",
